             was indicted for <rs id="t18040912-17-off100" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18040912-17-off100" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18040912-17-off100" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t18040912-17-cd101" type="crimeDate">24th of August</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18040912-17-off100 t18040912-17-cd101"></join>, a plane, value 10 d. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18040912-17-victim258" type="victimName">
                           James 
                           Bateman
                        <interp inst="t18040912-17-victim258" type="surname" value="Bateman"></interp>
